{"tid":2510148,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"六四未經批准集結案 黃之鋒岑敖暉袁嘉蔚梁凱晴認罪 朱凱廸仍需時考慮答辯方向","createTime":"2021-04-30T03:00:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T04:54:02.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"92a04087de5dcfc5291428ba5cb97091afeee49d","tid":2510148,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T03:00:44.000Z","msg":"去年警方禁止維園六四燭光集會，惟支聯會及大批市民堅持到維園紀念，其後支聯會主席李卓人、副主席何俊仁、多名常委以及壹傳媒集團創辦人黎智英等24人被控煽惑他人參與未經批准集結罪，以及參與一個未經批准集結等罪。其中朱凱廸、黃之鋒、岑敖暉、袁嘉蔚及梁凱晴五人早前透過律師表示擬承認參與未經批准集結罪。區域法院法官陳廣池今開庭處理，其中四人維持認罪答辯，而朱凱廸則表示仍在考慮中。控方現向認罪四人讀出承認案情。<br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒、岑敖暉、袁嘉蔚及梁凱晴今早承認明知而參與未經批准集結罪。控方申請將四人的案件合併，獲法官批准。控方遂向四人讀出承認案情。<br />\n<br />\n朱凱廸則透過代表大狀表示，仍需時考慮是否認罪，要求將案件押後再訊。法官遂將朱的案件押後至6月11日，與其餘未認罪的被告一同再訊。朱因涉違反國安法，仍須繼續還柙。<br />\n<br />\n朱凱廸今早精神不俗，於被告欄內向觀眾席方向打眼色。代表朱的資深大律師夏偉志表示，朱仍然在考慮答辯方向，故申請押後案件，獲法官批准。散庭後，朱從被告欄走進羈留室，多名旁聽人士高呼：「撐住呀！」「我哋掛住你呀，廸！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210430/G7FBCZNJANDX5FVWDQ5QPJHBNQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210430%2FG7FBCZNJANDX5FVWDQ5QPJHBNQ%2F&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnTyBzIW6ugq8wWEqYO2LRYLo%3D&h=df6d94a2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210430%2FG7FBCZNJANDX5FVWDQ5QPJHBNQ%2F&h=1d0388c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210430/G7FBCZNJANDX5FVWDQ5QPJHBNQ/</a>"},{"pid":"ae8b342c333e058bdfc8a6bf840ceb8eda8813c0","tid":2510148,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T03:18:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15362\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F15362&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnTyBzIW6ugq8wWEqYO2LRYLo%3D&h=55f1e5c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15362</a><br />\n<br />\n#區域法院第卅二庭 #英語聆訊<br />\n#陳廣池法官 #聆取對控罪的回答<br />\n👥梁凱睛,岑敖暉,黃之鋒,袁家蔚 #20200604維園<br />\n🛑岑敖暉,袁家蔚因另案而被還押逾1個月，黃之鋒因另案服刑中🛑<br />\n<br />\n控罪：參與未經批准集結<br />\n4人被控於2020年6月4日，在香港維多利亞公園，連同同案其他被告及其他不詳人士，明知而參與未經批准集結。<br />\n===================<br />\n控方申請把案件合併，辯方沒有反對。<br />\n<br />\n‼️4人認罪‼️<br />\n<br />\n11:06 休庭至11:30"},{"pid":"00f7734a87f7c0aff18dca05b6c0865abbb72c5f","tid":2510148,"uid":51820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T03:20:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3dc22354831bd2667e1e13e067530ac6870b9513","tid":2510148,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T03:21:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbd9564a5be44c3828d54f30de80595e1c7de6fc","tid":2510148,"uid":261913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T03:21:55.000Z","msg":"無人再去六四集會 共產黨唔會仲驚咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a532a74f815e2dc9b233505563f25c1a9bb6179b","tid":2510148,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T03:23:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20a74336f905c8f95cb9a2824cbb4dddb9a95e00","tid":2510148,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T03:51:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cab5af7738917ada3c70894df7d1a7b81b3e2d4","tid":2510148,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T03:51:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c7f3f515fb4d5bcd91c6c7f86d72d003db08331","tid":2510148,"uid":166474,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T03:54:39.000Z","msg":"之鋒而家冇晒鬥志, 告乜都認罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1b5dcecb6003861ae4dd3faa366df930961748a","tid":2510148,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T03:55:27.000Z","msg":"政治迫害"},{"pid":"c35bdd9412ca491b1710e971b883a8e5f5881029","tid":2510148,"uid":37992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c7f3f515fb4d5bcd91c6c7f86d72d003db08331","tid":2510148,"uid":166474,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T03:54:39.000Z","msg":"之鋒而家冇晒鬥志, 告乜都認罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T03:57:07.000Z","msg":"唔認罰得仲甘<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b3d3dece6b001f50d138d8ce376952ae9340a35","tid":2510148,"uid":71635,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4c7f3f515fb4d5bcd91c6c7f86d72d003db08331","tid":2510148,"uid":166474,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T03:54:39.000Z","msg":"之鋒而家冇晒鬥志, 告乜都認罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T03:58:58.000Z","msg":"認唔認罪都會輸硬<br />\n點解唔認黎減1／3刑<br />\n係呢個一拳話事社會<br />\n法治已經係笑話"},{"pid":"c2fe3532494bee186b1a323651daef2cbe989494","tid":2510148,"uid":74368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c7f3f515fb4d5bcd91c6c7f86d72d003db08331","tid":2510148,"uid":166474,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T03:54:39.000Z","msg":"之鋒而家冇晒鬥志, 告乜都認罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T04:07:13.000Z","msg":"人地同律師睇過晒先認架啦"},{"pid":"1e4e8810bdc801ea45a2fcc18ad239bdd92873b0","tid":2510148,"uid":55317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T04:10:11.000Z","msg":"之鋒而家點<br />\n<br />\n有冇好憔悴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d29cc9b93b41a979d24d089eacd6f3bdba09db8","tid":2510148,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T04:15:04.000Z","msg":"簡易版案情：<br />\n在2020年4月23日，蔡耀昌代表香港市民，由支聯會提交通知書予警方，申請在2020年6月4日19:00至22:00時在維多利亞公園舉行約有50000至100000名人公眾集會，目的是為了悼念六四事件。<br />\n<br />\n在2020年5月18日，支聯會與其他代表舉行聯合會議，商討集會安排。在2020年5月28日，衛生署在評估後不建議支聯會在2020年6月4日舉行集會，理由如下：<br />\n<br />\n⭐️在2020年5月27日有1067宗武漢肺炎個案，而且在同年3月中至4月頭個案急升及出現不同群組個案，亦在同年5月13至14日期間有3宗源頭不明的武漢肺炎個案，可見社區有隱性傳播鏈及未被發現的病人，令社區出現大規模爆發的風險<br />\n<br />\n⭐️政府在2020年1月25日，因應武漢肺炎帶來的健康風險，將應變級別定為緊急。他們希望市民可以保持適當社交距離，以降低社區出現爆發的風險<br />\n<br />\n⭐️就活動而言，衛生署認為支聯會難以規官所有人帶口罩，保持1.5社交距離，為每人探測體溫，保持8人一組及要求每個8人組別相距1.5米。加上萬一出現確診者，衛生署將難以追蹤患者。<br />\n<br />\n在2020年6月1日，警務處處長向支聯會發信，禁止集會舉行，以保障公共秩序，公共安全及保障市民的權利，以下是他們的考慮：<br />\n<br />\n⭐️599G條例當時的生效期是2020年5月22日至2020年6月4日<br />\n<br />\n⭐️武漢肺炎是高傳染性及潛伏期長的疾病，對市民的健康帶來高風險<br />\n<br />\n⭐️若批准六四集會，因有大型聚集，會提升武漢肺炎的傳染風險，有機會對所有市民帶來危害<br />\n<br />\n支聯會及後沒有就此決定上訴。<br />\n<br />\n在2020年6月4日，警方在16:00至17:00時在不同地方設置揚聲器，以通知市民六四集會以被禁止，若參與該集會，即是參與未經批准集會及違反599G。而康文署也有17:00時作出廣播，大概內容為要求市民遵守599G，若違反將會被檢控。當時康文署考慮到武漢肺炎的情況，關閉了2個足球場。<br />\n<br />\n(待續...)"},{"pid":"9cfb44d19eb8e687fb388e5bb0ed87b1701e6b38","tid":2510148,"uid":301952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cbd9564a5be44c3828d54f30de80595e1c7de6fc","tid":2510148,"uid":261913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T03:21:55.000Z","msg":"無人再去六四集會 共產黨唔會仲驚咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T04:17:28.000Z","msg":"點解共產黨要驚你香港人唔去六四集會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5432ef43bc2ab055d939b8b0c4976bb38a5a8d1a","tid":2510148,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T04:44:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23b73e46fec1e16b32b67539fc08196164a0d7fb","tid":2510148,"uid":261913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9cfb44d19eb8e687fb388e5bb0ed87b1701e6b38","tid":2510148,"uid":301952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cbd9564a5be44c3828d54f30de80595e1c7de6fc","tid":2510148,"uid":261913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T03:21:55.000Z","msg":"無人再去六四集會 共產黨唔會仲驚咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T04:17:28.000Z","msg":"點解共產黨要驚你香港人唔去六四集會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T04:54:02.000Z","msg":"大中華膠集會黎 本土派點會再去六四集會<br />\n都無人當自己係中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}